118
00:12:12,063 --> 00:12:14,666
Lucky guesses. False positives.

119
00:12:14,766 --> 00:12:19,604
If you let yourself fall victim
to a belief bias of any kind,

120
00:12:19,704 --> 00:12:23,374
that's when you start forcing
