00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:32,243
And her pain was consistent.

138
00:13:32,789 --> 00:13:34,245
It was chronic.

139
00:13:35,293 --> 00:13:37,482
It was enough
that my husband and I decided

140
00:13:37,582 --> 00:13:39,851
that she shouldn't be
